Package: nva
Title: R Client for the Norwegian National Research Archive (NVA) API
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Roar", "Bakken Stovner", , "robast@oslomet.no", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for accessing the Norwegian National Research
    Archive (NVA) API. Includes support for searching publications, retrieving
    metadata, accessing Cristin data, and downloading files.
